Details:
We Have Branches At:Cunnigham Road, Residency Road, Jaynagar, Vijayanagar, Marathahalli, Koramangala, Indranagar, RT Nagar, bhanargatta Road,Fazor Town, HRBR Layout, HSR Layout,Malleshwaram, new DEL Road, Rajaji nagar, Ram murthy nagar, Vidhyaranpura, GOV College, Carmel college, Jyothinivas College, Sindi college, Mount Carme College, st Joseph college, st Joseph main collegeOur ObjectivesTo equip our students with the right skill sets to bring about a transformation in their analytical, critical and logical thinking. Giraffe is an autonomous private coaching and tutorial centre that prepares and counsels academically qualified students to pursue right careers in the field of Science, Medicine, Engineering and Humanities.
Student ProfileBesides, the student, with a firm eye on a career, Giraffe also welcomes the serious amateur with a discerning eye and a creative mind, who is willing to devote the time and effort. Giraffe appreciates the skills owned by the students but the teaching philosophy at Giraffe is that, the institute takes it a duty to see that students have the requisite knowledge and confidence. Students are taught all the skills they require. However, our ideal is not so much to teach a student, as to help him learn.
Academic PrinciplesThe most important qualities imparted through Giraffe's academic approach are the abilities to think independently and holistically. We promote the idea of innovation and to learn through creative exploration and experimentation. No exam result can depend solely on an institute or its faculty. Giraffe Learning has traditionally provided exceptional depth of educational experience, including interactive learning; a focus on creative problem solving, and opportunities for experimentation and research. To broaden the curricular experience, the approach is to integrate all the learning to enhance practical thinking in students. The overall structure of Giraffe's program is a combination of theory, skills, tips and methodologies to crack any kind of tough examination.
Instruction MethodologyGiraffe follows a unique highly acclaimed instruction method (D-I-V-E) where, right from inception a student is encouraged to learn by experimenting with all different aspects of a problem. Students are encouraged to innovate and evolve solutions as they tackle problems from first principles. Solutions are rarely spoon fed to students; rather the student discovers his own methodologies by creative problem solving. 
Both rational and critical techniques are evolved and refined with each subsequent assignment & test - to finally peak with the main mock examination. The main focus of any coaching session is not just to impart information but also to see that students get the utmost invaluable tips & methodologies of answering examinations. It is not always the most knowledgeable who get the most marks - but rather the best prepared. Our emphasis is to let students exercise their analytical skills and show them to follow some simple and quick specific principles.
ManagementOur promoters are alumni of IIT, which gives students unsurpassed experience in taking & excelling at entrance exams. (Anybody with experience in tackling the IIT entrance exam. can probably handle any exam anywhere ). 
The management team at Giraffe includes Professors and teachers with over 15 yrs of expertise teaching and coaching at both national and state levels. Faculty include authors of famous text books, as well as those who have set the actual Board, CET & IIT exams.
AdministrationWell-trained, experienced and quality counsellors take care of complete admission procedure. Along with that we have Department and Centre Co-ordinators who take care of individual student's needs, problems, concerns and feedback. Giraffe assimilates the best of practices, which include Attendance follow-up, Personal Co-ordination, Marks Records, Reviews on their performance to students and parents, Appreciation Program, to keep up the motivation levels in students. These activities make Giraffe the best both at administration and academics.
Infrastructure FacilitiesGiraffe Learning has state of the art infrastructure to conduct their coaching sessions smoothly meeting their entire end-to-end requirements. It has well- designed and elaborate classroom for training sessions. Giraffe Centers across Bangalore, so students do not have to spend precious time travelling. Giraffe Spacious classrooms. Giraffe Proper and comfortable seating arrangements. Giraffe Extensive course material specifically written with the actual exam in mind.

Details: Jamboree is the oldest institute in India and the best of its kind, which offers comprehensive classroom preparation programs for tests such as GMAT, GRE, SAT, TOEFLTM and IELTS. Jamboree centres are present in 14 cities of India and in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and Kathmandu . Each centre follows a uniform curriculum and has outstanding faculty, all of whom are trained in our head office. Each centre offers the same teaching standards and syllabus.At Jamboree, the most trusted name in India for education abroad, we help you give shape to your career and dreams. Founded in 1993, Jamboree attempted to fill the information gap on education abroad. Back then, the only information available on education abroad was through friends and family living or studying abroad. Thus, only a small percentage of interested students had access to information. Jamboree attempted to fill this information gap. Now when we in 'Team Jamboree' reflect on the past few years, we see thousands of our students on the thresholds of careers that would not have been possible without the right guidance at the right time.Jamboree, known for its thorough research and professionalism, is a one-stop shop for education abroad.Jamboree makes the entire process of studying abroad, from preparing to actually joining a foreign university, a smooth process. In recent years, the inclusion of several value-added services such as discounted couriers, educational loans and pre-departure orientation has made Jamboree Education Pvt. Ltd. a one-stop solution centre for all your study abroad requirements.

Name: USA Univquest
Services Offered: Coaching & Tuitions , USA Education Consultants , SAT Coaching ,
Details: With the globalization of the economy in India and the growing affluence of its large middle class, studying in developed countries like USA, UK, Canada & all European countries has become a very viable option for tens and thousands of Indian Students at the Undergraduate Level.The major reasons cited for this increase are - better quality of education, cultural diversity, building up a cosmopolitan outlook, flexibility and wide range of courses / careers to pick from and, above all, unmatched research and development facilities available across all courses in these countries. A large number of well-qualified and financially able Indian students are interested in opportunities for higher education in USA.Studying abroad can certainly improve your employment prospects. An increased proficiency in English or another major language is just one of the many advantages. Add that to a developing awareness of different cultures, an increase in your own self-confidence, an extensive network of new colleagues and your new higher education qualification, and you'll have the edge that many employers are looking for. The overriding view from employers is that if you have an excellent academic track record, your nationality is no barrier to your future employment. In fact, if you can demonstrate a real passion to work in an international environment, bringing with you the qualification and skills you gained while studying abroad, you will very often be more attractive to employers than others around you.International graduates are seen as huge assets by international employers in many sectors, from knowledge based industries like consulting and banking to global industries like health care, consumer product and automotive, as well as governmentall seeking to establish a globally minded cadre of young administrators. Many international employers now focus on building relationships with universities and business schools to target the crme-de-la-crme of international graduates. The most straightforward source of entry for international students into companies is through internship programs. This allows employers the opportunity to view candidates at close hand, without having to complete all the formal visa requirements for full-time hiring.  Contact us for further details.

Chartered Accountants are the ones who are specialised in accountancy, auditing and taxation which are a few to say about.  Chartered Accountancy ( CA) is a professional course in Accounting introduced in our country in 1949 with the enactment of The Chartered Accountants Act. The governing body of this course is named as The Institute of Chartered Accountants of India.  CA program structure currently has three sections, the first one being Common Proficiency Test (CPT), the second one being The Integrated Professional Competency Course (IPCC) and the last being FINAL examination. Details: ICICIdirect Centre for Financial Learning (ICFL) is an educational initiative of ICICI Securities Ltd. ICFL is committed to enhance financial literacy amongst all existing and prospective stake holders in the society by empowering them to make better & more informed decisions. ICFL is also committed to lead the path to create next generation leaders who could catalyze the growth of financial markets in India by expanding the pool of qualified & certified professionals for the industry. ICFL training programmes are categorized under : 1. Investment Education 2. Professional Certification and Development. Over the period, ICFL has trained more than 2.5 lakh students and investors across India through one or more programmes. The repository of domain knowledge includes host of in-house developed seminars, workshops, certifications and training programmes leading to reputed certifications. ICFL has offices and training facilities across India aided by technological capability/ alliances to deliver trainings through classroom, eLearning, virtual classroom and satellite classrooms.

Details: ASAP Tutor Pvt. Ltd. is a subsidiary of ASAP Tutor, Inc., operating www.asaptutor.com in the US. ASAP Tutor, Inc. was originally established in 2005 to teach math online to high school and college students in North America. Since the beginning of its operations, we have received tremendous support from many students and have received frequent requests to expand our subjects and cover more geographic areas.Following these requests and demand, we opened Classroom Coaching (CC) in Bangalore, India where we have our online operation base for ASAP Tutor Inc. In addition to classroom coaching, we started Correspondence Classroom Coaching (CCC) in 2009. This Correspondence Classroom Coaching is the first program of this kind in India by which students can receive lectures by experienced teachers at home just like they do at Coaching centers. This innovative program frees students from time and troubles of commuting and enabled students to access the finest classroom coaching no matter where they live.We are committed to education in India very much. As a company looking at huge potential of Indian people in the US, we know that the success of many Indian people in the US comes from peoples commitment to the education. The aspirations of such people and parents have made us start coaching center and innovative correspondence course program. We are committed to KNOWLEDGE ENHANCEMENT in India.To guarantee the best coaching education to our students, we are making continuous improvement in classroom teaching and management. For example, our teachers always check their teaching by monitoring the recorded class. We are recording most of our lectures on DVDs that both students and parents can rent. We are very serious about quality management. We believe in education for ANYONE, ANYTIME and ANYWHERE.It will be our pleasure to have an opportunity to join hands with you in enhancing the academic career of your child. We are happy to assist your children to achieve great academic success.

Details:
Anatomy Guru has been the go-to location for medical tutoring in Hyderabad, Salem and Bangalore for over 10 years, and we lo...ok forward to many more years of serving our budding doctors community. Founded in Hyderabad in 2003 with a vision for high-quality and meaningful one-to-one tutoring relationships, Anatomy Guru moved near Salem, Tamil Nadu in 2009 and to its current location at Bangalore in 2011.With over 10 years' experience in placing home, personal, one-to-one tutors, you can be sure that our thorough profiling and personalized service will match you with the right personal medical tutor to fulfill the specific educational needs of you or your budding medico. Trusted and always highly recommended, we have helped hundreds of young people and adults on the path to academic success.Our Approach
Anatomy Guru provides students with individualized medical tutoring programs catered to each students specific situation, learning style, and unique needs and goals. Our philosophy is that all students are capable learners and we choose the right medical tutor and design our approach to stimulate each students learning. We sometimes arrange tutoring in small groups, but we favor a one-to-one ratio that allows us to focus on the unique learning process of one individual. All programs begin with an intake interview in which we set up a unique program based on each students specific academic goals.
Our medical tutors take confidential notes after each tutoring session, and share those notes with families, if needed. Our administrators consult these notes frequently to ensure that each students needs are being met, and we encourage parents to follow their students progress through our tutors as well.
We carefully select our teaching faculty from a large pool of applicants, based on expertise in subject matter and experience teaching students of different ages and varying learning styles. Our medical tutors have been chosen for their minds as well as for their intuition, patience, adaptability, and attention to detail. Our tutors have demonstrated success in their role as medical tutor and mentor. Students benefit greatly, both academically and personally, from the special attention our tutors provide. From Hyderabad to Bangalore, medical tutoring is Anatomy Gurus passion, and we hope you will find the experience as rewarding as we do."

Details:
Manya Education (P) Ltd. (MEPL) was set up in 2002 as a first of its kind, one-stop solution provider in overseas education. Named after one of the 1008 avatars of Goddess Saraswati, Manya signifies the free flow of wisdom and consciousness while discriminating between wrong and right. In the last decade, MEPL has successfully established itself as the national leader in three broad domains namely
- Study abroad test preparation
- Overseas admissions
- Skill building especially in language and communication training.MEPL is the Indian partner and the most successful International Division of The Princeton Review (TPR), the worlds leading test preparation service provider for tests such as the GMAT, GRE, SAT, IELTS and TOEFL. The Princeton Review was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Framingham, MA. With a presence in 1000+ classroom locations over 17 countries, it has been a pioneer and leader, in helping students achieve their higher education goals for 30 years through college and graduate school test preparation and private tutoring. With more than 165 print and digital publications, the company provides students and their parents with the resources to research, apply to, prepare for, and learn how to pay for higher education. The Princeton Review partners with schools and guidance counselors throughout the US to assist in college readiness, test preparation and career planning services, helping more students pursue post-secondary education.Princeton Review has these 4 centers in Bangalore city:The Princeton Review, Koramangala

Details:
Farida HB is a Handwriting Analyst and Grapho analytical therapist. After practicing the handwriting changes on herself, she says, I feel like a new person. My way of tackling situations and looking at problems has changed. My relationships with my family have improved beyond expectations. I thank the Almighty for bringing this science to my notice and my family for supporting me in taking it to a new dimension. I hope that you to will benefit from it .Handwriting Analysis is the study of relationship between handwriting and personality. Handwriting analysis can quickly reveal such factors as your character, emotions, intellect, creativity, social adjustment, your desires, fears, weaknesses, strengths and sexual appetite just to mention a few.It saves you time in accurately finding out all about a person.Our handwriting therapy programs are developed especially for students to help them write legibly, effectively, and with speed. Here we teach students how to form and join alphabet with good quality flow. We provide form of instructions with specific learning requirements of the students. Spotlight is given on Grapho Therapy, sitting posture, notebook position, pen/pencil grip control and joining of the letters. During the course special attention is given on each letter formation as this will result in positive impact on words and sentence formation.

Each office is supported by well qualified professionals and education experts and works towards guiding Indian students in their admission requirements for overseas study.
Not only have we trained students in admission tests but have also helped over 2000 students set foot in a University of their choice across the world by means of our personalized coaching and counseling services through our locations across the country - major cities being Delhi, Bangalore, Mumbai, Kolkata, Pune etc. Backed by the expertise and strong industry connections of WLC College, our students have also found suitable placements with ease while still studying in foreign countries.
Be it Engineering, Medicine, Bio-technology, Law, Business Management, Fashion, Media, Art and Design or Hospitality to name a few, our end to end services have the best partners for studying in any destination overseas. Our major partners are spread mostly in UK, USA, New Zealand, Australia, Germany and Canada.
Thousands of satisfied and successful students bear testimony to the quality of our service and the missionary zeal of our consultants.
Not surprisingly, our students have landed in the most prestigious universities for the most sought after courses. This is further certified by the fact that the number of students availing our services is increasing with each passing day. Our reliability ensures flawless admission process and total satisfaction not only for the students but also for the partnering Universities.

Details: We at TNTLI believe that every child has hidden potential and every child has right to a stress free and confident life when they finish their Schooling Years. In contrast to our belief, the reality is that students suffer a lot due to peer pressure to perform well in academics once they pass their schooling. In such externally governed environment, students have to compromise their jubilant teenage hood to outperform in academics without exploiting their real potential. When we researched the causes for this environment, we found that maximum of student's time in well established academic training centers is spent on revising the concepts again and again which they have already learnt in their schooling years. The further research revealed that if student has his foundations strong, cracking any competitive examination just needs optimum practice on applications; and self study is the KEY to success. Name: Quickstep English Center
Services Offered: Spoken English Classes ,
Details:
Quickstep was founded in 1995 as a training organization offering various skills training programmes to adults. It began in R.T. Nagar, Bangalore and continues to operate there.
We are an ISO 9001:2008 Certified organization.
We have also received accreditation by National Accreditation Board for educational providers (NABET)-Quality Council of India. We are only one in the training and educational sectors in Bangalore and also in Karnataka.
We are one of the few education and training organization in India who have received this accreditation. This accreditation is recognized by Government of India.
We are also the only approved institute in Karnataka registered with NIELIT (National Institute of Electronics & Information Technology) Department of Electronics & IT (DeitY) Government of India, o conduct IT Literacy courses viz. BCC and CCC of the NIELIT.
Quickstep is also the registered trade mark of the group, consisting of several organizations, each specializing in an area related to training. A common theme for all the members of Quickstep group is to upgrade job skills of the students.Quickstep has also a publishing organization, Book Direct, as a member of the group. Book Direct prints and publishes books and CDs required for own use of the training organizations. These are also sold in the market through booksellers. Quickstep has also promoted another organization, Institute of Adventure Promotion, which trains young people in adventure tourism and conducts adventure treks in Himalayan regions, and also organizes local treks.
* Quickstep offers training in the areas of:
(i) English (ii) Soft skills (iii) Call Centre training  International and Domestic
(iv) Finishing courses for Engineering and Management students (v) Foreign languages 
(vi) Computer courses (vi) Accounts and Tally (vii) Retail industry (ix) Corporate training
 
* Specialized Courses :
Cambridge ESOL Certificate Examination
1. BEC(Business English Certificate) Course
2. IELTS(International English Language Testing System)
3. TOFEL(Test of English as a Foreign Language)
International StudentsEach year Quickstep trains a large number of overseas students from all over the world. The courses are customized to meet the needs of the students who come to India to learn English as a foreign language, ITes training etc.
Appreciation for QuickstepQuickstep has been able to earn the trust of students and well-known organizations. For instance Hitachi Ltd, a Japanese giant global company has arrangements with Quickstep to train their employees in language skills. At the moment employees from their Tokyo office are undergoing training at our R.T.Nagar branch.Quickstep has conducted hundreds of training programmes for MNCs, reputed Indian companies, PSUs, government departments, colleges and NGOs. We also sometimes assist them in recruitment at the interview stage. A list of some of these organizations is available in the enclosed brochure.The highly respected newspaper, The Wall Street Journal, in its March 2, 2010 article on Indias Aspiring English Speakers covered Quickstep English Centre. The WSJ zeroed in on English Centre, among all other such institutes in India, to do the article. The article was based on interviews with our students and members of faculty. Here is the Link:
(http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704761004575096304215359756.html? mod=WSJ_ipinion_LEFTTopBucket)

Few decades back, it was quite simple to gain admission to any course you desired in a college of your choice. It is no more the case. There are hundreds or thousands of students waiting in line for admission in any top ranked institute. There are various competitive exams to be mastered if you want to enter into a good institute or into attractive and coveted Government jobs.Students and graduates are working hard than ever before to achieve their dreams. We at Competitive Success have you in mind and all the resources we provide here are aimed at making your preparation easier. The resources that are made available here have been carefully selected. The training materials and the sample tests are designed considering the syllabus and toughness of the exam. As the education system is undergoing changes, there are policy changes occurring on the entrance tests and the eligibility criteria too. It is often confusing when there is any change on policy. Without a clear guidance, students and candidates are often left in a lurch.We aim to provide clear instructions and details on all exams. Here you can find all details including the eligibility criteria for each exam, syllabus for each exam and other necessary information a candidate should possess. This is a comprehensive resource on all competitive exams. The exams that are covered here are not limited to a particular field. Whatever be your choice of study or career, you can be sure that we have resources for the particular exam. The materials that are provided here will help you in preparing for the exam and to acquire and master the required skills. Practice is a factor which often differentiates the topper from the rest of the candidates. We offer you a variety of sample tests so that you can be prepared for your exams. You can sign up with us for free. There is absolutely no hidden charges or fees involved in signing up. So, sign up and start your exam preparations today. We wish you happy study times!!!

Details: Entuze has been founded by a team of professionals from diverse fields connected by a common passion for Simplifying Learning. Our founders, having grown up in India, have experienced first-hand how the traditional education system tries to fit students into a predefined mould and encourages rote learning. They have deeply analysed the qualities that differentiates some of the inspirational teachers they have had in their lives and concluded that good teachers have the ability to simplify concepts, they carry the entire class and their lectures are engaging and fun. The founding team has explored ways to leverage technology to take some of these qualities to a wider audience. The team has also delved into different learning styles of individuals and has built the notion of Multiple Intelligence into Entuzes offerings. Entuze creates engaging educational content that simplifies concepts and delivers such content in multiple modes, recognising the varied learning styles and cognitive abilities of individuals. Entuze has developed an Intelligent Learning Platform (ILP) that can create individualised learning paths after assessing the relative strengths and weaknesses of a student. Entuzes Intelligent Learning Platform can cater to a wide spectrum of educational segments. Our first offering: CA CPT Module is for students who are planning to take the Common Proficiency Test (CPT) conducted by the Council of the Institute Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI). Contact us for more details
